{
  "texts": [
    "With AI and DL's growth, convincing multimedia manipulations have become easier, leading to concerns about their malicious use.",
    "Deepfakes, covering a range of techniques like facial synthesis and identity swaps, complicate effective detection [33].",
    "Beyond entertainment, deepfakes pose serious security threats, enabling political impersonation and misinformation dissemination.",
    "Federated learning (FL) and blockchain [34] offer promising solutions.",
    "FL allows ML model training while preserving data privacy [35][36][37], and blockchain ensures data trustworthiness by authenticating source data and enhancing deepfake detection."
  ]
}